WEBVTT

00:01:25.752 --> 00:01:31.373
qadimgi yunon tarixchisi Plutarx 
'kema afsonasi'ni aytib bergan.

00:01:31.373 --> 00:01:34.207
Xo'sh, qanday qilib siz "men"siz?

00:01:34.207 --> 00:01:38.669
Aytishlariga ko'ra, Tesey afsonaviy 
Afina qiroli,

00:01:38.669 --> 00:01:43.161
Krit orolidagi yovuz Minotaurni yolg'iz 
mag'lub etadi

00:01:43.161 --> 00:01:45.757
va kemada uyga qaytib keladi.

00:01:45.757 --> 00:01:47.656
Bu qahramonlikni abadiylashtirishga,

00:01:47.656 --> 00:01:54.394
ming yil davomida afinaliklar, imkoni 
boricha, kemani portda ushlab turishga

00:01:54.394 --> 00:01:58.285
harakat qilishdi va har yili ular 
qahramonning yo'lini bosib o'tardilar.

00:01:58.285 --> 00:02:01.319
Kemaning qismlari eskirsa yoki buzilsa, 
ularning o'rnini